15 SECTION 16. Updating bylaws. (1) No later than January 1, 2027, the Oregon Transpor-
16 tation Commission shall conduct a review and amend its bylaws.
17 (2) The bylaws of the commission must include:
18 (a) A requirement that an electronic mail address for each voting member of the com-
19 mission be published on the commission’s website; and
20 (b) A process for ensuring that meeting materials for forthcoming decisions by the
21 commission are published with reasonable notice prior to public comment deadlines to allow
22 for review and engagement by the public on matters that may impact the public.
23 (3) No later than September 15, 2027, the commission shall submit to the committees or
24 interim committees of the Legislative Assembly related to transportation a report on the
25 changes made during the review and amendment of its bylaws.
26 SECTION 17. Section 16 of this 2026 Act is repealed on January 2, 2028.
