14 (e) Links to all available county and city transportation project websites.
15 (f) Links to websites about transportation projects receiving moneys from the Connect Oregon
16 Fund.
17 SECTION 20. The section captions used in this 2026 Act are provided only for the con-
18 venience of the reader and do not become part of the statutory law of this state or express
19 any legislative intent in the enactment of this 2026 Act.
20 SECTION 21. This 2026 Act being necessary for the immediate preservation of the public
21 peace, health and safety, an emergency is declared to exist, and this 2026 Act takes effect
22 on its passage.
